## Privacy Policy
Last Updated: 17.04.2026
Surgery Turkey Guide ("we," "our," or "the app") respects the privacy of our users and takes the protection of personal data seriously. This privacy policy is designed to inform you about the information collected when you use our application and how that information is used.
## 1. Information Collected
Our application serves as a guide and is strictly communication-oriented. In this context, the following types of data may be processed:

* Contact Information: E-mail address or name shared when you contact us.
* Usage Data: Anonymous statistical data such as click rates within the app and viewed clinic pages.
* Device Information: Device model and operating system version to improve application performance.

## 2. Purpose of Using Information
The collected information is used for the following purposes:

* To provide information about clinics and healthcare services.
* To respond to user inquiries and provide support.
* To analyze application performance and fix technical issues.

## 3. AI Services and Data Sharing

Our application includes an AI-powered chat feature.

When you use the AI chat, the content you provide (such as messages, questions, or other inputs) may be transmitted to a third-party AI service provider (such as OpenAI) in order to generate responses.

This data is processed by the third-party provider solely for the purpose of delivering AI-generated responses within the app.

We do not use this data for advertising purposes. However, we do not control how third-party providers process or store data. These providers are responsible for handling your data in accordance with their own privacy policies.

Users are advised not to share sensitive personal information, including health data, financial information, or personally identifiable information, while using the AI chat feature.


## 4. Third-Party Links
Our application may contain links to clinics' phone numbers, websites, or social media accounts. Surgery Turkey Guide is not responsible for the privacy policies or practices of these external links/third parties.
## 5. Medical Disclaimer
Surgery Turkey Guide is not a medical institution. The information provided within the application is for informational purposes only and does not substitute professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Always seek the advice of a physician or other qualified health provider with any questions you may have regarding a medical condition.
## 6. Data Security
We take industry-standard measures to ensure the security of your data. However, please remember that no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.
## 7. Children's Privacy
Our application is not intended for children under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal data from children.
